| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3017 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d9bc5526-bbb7-55d1-8c6a-a832c52a2995"
